replies.body:
My issue is his power against melee champs in top, I'm seen a lot of top players lose to Urgot due to his range and tankiness from the start. Some think he needs a nerf, I'm not one of them, but he is unfair when you play against a melee champ such as Poppy or a squishy semi-top laner such as Azir. Right now, I feel he's fine, just a new skin to show he still exists would be nice to you Urgot mains!
~~Star Guardian Urgot for the win!~~
{{sticker:poppy-wink}}
